section_summary: The text is a speech given by Ahmed Al-Saadoun, the President of the National Assembly, expressing gratitude to the members of the council and acknowledging the responsibility that comes with their consensus. He also thanks Daoud Marafi for his nomination and subsequent withdrawal. Al-Saadoun emphasizes the importance of the Kuwaiti people's role in the political life of Kuwait and their response to the call for elections. He reflects on his own experience in the council and highlights the achievements of the Kuwaiti people in the recent elections. The text also includes information about the legislative session and its topics.
